<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb8b48ceb-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea" identifier="/us/usc/t5/s7502"><num value="7502">§ 7502.</num><heading> Actions covered</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This subchapter applies to a suspension for 14 days or less, but does not apply to a suspension under section 7521 or 7532 of this title or any action initiated under <ref href="/us/usc/t5/s1215">section 1215 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb8b48cec-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/95/454/tII/s204/a">Pub. L. 95–454, title II, § 204(a)</ref>, <date date="1978-10-13">Oct. 13, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/1135">92 Stat. 1135</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/101/12/s9/a/2">Pub. L. 101–12, § 9(a)(2)</ref>, <date date="1989-04-10">Apr. 10, 1989</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/103/35">103 Stat. 35</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idb8b48ced-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">
